Access-Network-Identifier Option in DHCP
2016", shape=ellipse, fillcolor="#e8f0ff", tooltip="This document specifies the format and mechanism that is to be used for encoding Access-Network Identifiers in DHCPv4 and DHCPv6 messages by defining new Access-Network-Identifier options and sub-options."]; 

